mlflex.tcga
Class TcgaSomaticMutationDataProcessor

java.lang.Object
  mlflex.AbstractDataProcessor
      mlflex.tcga.AbstractTcgaDataProcessor
          mlflex.tcga.TcgaSomaticMutationDataProcessor

public class TcgaSomaticMutationDataProcessor
extends AbstractTcgaDataProcessor

This data processor is designed to parse information from the TCGA somatic-mutation data. This data can be downloaded from http://tcga-data.nci.nih.gov/tcga/dataAccessMatrix.htm. This code has so far been tested only on the glioblastoma multiforme data.

Author:
Stephen Piccolo

GetPriorKnowledgeSelectedFeatures

protected java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> GetPriorKnowledgeSelectedFeatures()
Description copied from class: AbstractDataProcessor
If the "PriorKnowledge" feature-selection approach is used, a hand-selected list of features for each data processor must be specified. In this case, this method should be overridden, and the values should be returned.

Overrides:
GetPriorKnowledgeSelectedFeatures in class AbstractDataProcessor
Returns:
A list of features that are believed (perhaps based on prior studies or a literature search) to be most relevant for classification.
